[1:] Who/what are your mains?
- Astride Survival/Beast Mastery Hunter lvl 80 (Whisperwind Server)

[2:] Which alts were your favorite this year?
- Diirn lvl 23 NE Druid Balance spec
- Natrias Blood Elf DK (No specific spec yet)
- Velknut Tauren Druid Resto/Balance 
- Orcthwa Orc Warrior Fury Spec

[3:] How many characters did you get to 60? 70? 80?
- got Natrias to 60, Velk to 80, Orcthwa to 60. Astride to 80

[4:] What character are you most proud of and why?
- Astride and velknut. both are great. 


Around Azeroth

[5:] What was your biggest/most memorable achievement(s) this year? What was the most painful?
-Astride getting to 80. My dps still sucks

[6:] What has been the most fun raid/pve fight so far in WotLK?
- Naxxramas

[7:] What was your favorite quest/questchain?
- Argent Crusade quests

[8:] A lot of powerful lore has been introduced in this expansion. Any favorite bits?
- I like the cold weather flying, and knights of the ebon blade

[9:] The rise of the Lich King has changed Azeroth and its people so much. Who's your favorite NPC(s) in this expansion?
- Kel'Thuzad

[10:] Which in-game holiday was the most fun this year?
- anything really


Friends and Enemies

[11:] Did you change guilds this year? If so why?
- Well i changed Astride from Adventurers Inc, a guild that my friends and I formed, to a new raiding guild. Im happy with it sometimes. 

[12:] What was your guild's biggest/proudest accomplishment this year?
idk. i havent done much with them

[13:] Did you make a lot of new friends? Any mortal enemies?
- I have made a ton of new friends this year. A few enemies lol. 

[14:] Any fun or memorable PVP encounters?
- Not really. I don't do much pvp.


Looking Ahead

[15:] What changes are you most excited for in Cataclysm?
- The fact that ill be able to fly in azeroth

[16:] Which new race/class combos are you going to roll? Got any names yet?
- yes a worgen druid named seliesor

[17:] Where do you see your character in the next few months?
- Hopefully ill get astride to level up her cooking, and a few other professions

NO SLEEP LAST NIGHT! had to be here at 4 am! it fuckin sux!

Sometimes I just feel like completely giving up on life. Matt and I had a big fight last night. IT was over money. fuckin money! Im fed up with money. its all my life revolves around. Thats what we fight about all the time but this was the worst. I practically told him our marriage was over. I regret saying it. I love him with all my heart and all my soul but he just cant understand. But i think he is trying to at least. I paid off all my debt before we got married. He didnt know he was $15k in debt from fuckin school loans. I just dont know waht to do anymore you guys. Im sick of it. 

We are going into marriage counseling. We need it. Its going to save our marriage. I am going to continue taking my medicines. I am on zoloft and xanax. I am crying all the time. I am sooo incredibly sad. I am going to do my best to be able for him to trust me again. I know he loves me. 

I am gonna go. I need some advice. please give me some advice.

Please Pray
Current mood: pleased

I ask that each and everyone of you, no matter what race, religion, anything that you  are, that you please pray for me. I have had a rough couple of days.

Story behind it all:

Ok on Saturday I went with my mom and dad and my in-laws to Indiana to visit my grandparents and get some good homegrown veggies from their farm.  Mm good veggies. Well that night I got home and I was fine until about midnight. matt and i had been laying in bed. I couldnt get to sleep and I started having trouble breathing. My heart was beeating like amillion times a minute, i started to throw up, my vision went blurry. I was having a panic attack. I called my mother at 12:30 am and itook 2 aleve to make me sleep. Well that worked but the next day i was having trouble breathing still. it didnt help that i was on a boat out on lake michigan watching the air and water show. I get sick on boats. Luckily that didnt happen that day. Well lets just say monday i went to the doctor. They gave me xanax. Im happy but Ive had 5 in the past 29 hours. and its not good. I am going to the psychiatrist tomorrow for my depression and to tell him of these panic attacks. Its getting really bad and im afraid that they wont stop. I dont want to depend on the Xanax to help me. But if thats what it takes then i will have to deal with them.

I just ask each and everyone of you to pray for me. You can ask me any questions that you like.. I love comments. I am not doing this for attention. I have a loving husband who told me i should blog on it. He and my family and friends are worried about me. But please just pray for me that i get better and that I feel better. Well its time to take the meds and go back to sleep.

Gnite

Natalie
